item.description:
您当前尝试调用 API 的方式存在一些问题，我强烈建议阅读文档，因为它可以消除很多困惑。
话虽如此，下面是一个您可以使用的良好起点。

headers = {
&#39;Content-Type&#39;: &#39;application/json&#39;,
&#39;Authorization&#39;: f&quot;Bearer {os.environ.get(&#39;OPENAI_API_KEY&#39;)}&quot;
}

print(&quot;sending request&quot;)
payload = {
&#39;model&#39;: &#39;gpt-4o&#39;,
&#39;messages&#39;: [
{
&#39;role&#39;: &#39;system&#39;,
&#39;content&#39;: &#39;You are a helpful assistant.您将尽最大努力满足用户的要求。&#39;
},
{
&#39;role&#39;: &#39;user&#39;,
&#39;content&#39;: [
{&#39;type&#39;: &#39;text&#39;, &#39;text&#39;: &#39;描述此图像&#39;},
{&#39;type&#39;: &#39;image_url&#39;, &#39;image_url&#39;: {&#39;url&#39;: f&#39;data:image/jpeg;base64,{image_base64}&#39;}}
]
}
],
&#39;max_tokens&#39;: 800
}

response = request.post(&#39;https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions&#39;, headers=headers, json=payload)

text = response.json()[&#39;choices&#39;][0][&#39;message&#39;][&#39;content&#39;]
print(text)
